        },
        {
          "ability": {
            "ability_type": "offensive",
            "action_type": {
              "name": "One Action",
              "subtype": "action_type",
              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            "effect": "Vinn makes two unarmed Strikes. If both hit the same creature, combine their damage for the purpose of resistances and weaknesses. Apply Vinn's multiple attack penalty to the Strikes normally. When Vinn targets the same creature with both Strikes, if either Strike hits, the target must succeed at a DC 24 Fortitude save or be stunned 1 (stunned 3 on a critical failure). This is an incapacitation effect.   \nAlternatively, Vinn can replace one or both of his attacks during Flurry of Blows with Grapples, Repositions, Shoves, or Trips.",
